<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_8539dfce730d.aspx"><b>小雅·谷风</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson8539dfce730d">
<p>习习谷风，维风及雨。将恐将惧，维予与女。将安将乐，女转弃予。<br />习习谷风，维风及颓。将恐将惧，置予于怀。将安将乐，弃予如遗。<br />习习谷风，维山崔嵬。无草不死，无木不萎。忘我大德，思我小怨。</p>
</div>
